tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured laboratory values are within normal limits for this patient, including glucose metabolism, renal function, and electrolyte balance. No laboratory abnormalities detected; results are unremarkable from a clinical laboratory perspective. Continued routine monitoring is recommended.
